Media
Manga
Created by Saizō Harawata, Battle Game in 5 Seconds was first launched as a webcomic, and a remake illustrated by Kashiwa Miyako began publishing on Shogakukan's MangaONE app and Ura Sunday website on August 11 and August 18, 2015, respectively. In October 2024, Miyako announced that the manga would enter on hiatus due to health and personal issues since the start of the year, stating as well that the series is approaching its end. The series resumed on January 9, 2025. Shogakukan has collected its chapters into individual  volumes. The first volume was released on February 26, 2016. As of November 12, 2025, 29 volumes have been released.
Comikey is digitally publishing the manga in English since July 12, 2021.
